  <div id="text-content_1A144874-37A7-4D08-8C7C-EDEE8E2D5860" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If allowed, you can report a discussion reply in Discussions Redesign.</p>
<p><strong>Notes:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>When a reply is reported by a user, the user must indicate why the reply is being reported (inappropriate, offensive and/or abusive, or other). </li>
<li>Reporting a reply cannot be undone.</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-discussions" data-step-uuid="19c98876-b851-46e9-b80b-7cb9f270df05">
    <h2 id="open-discussions" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Discussions</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/698/372/original/7ceb249a-f097-442d-a986-f7b0f9d2a786.png" srcset="" alt="Open Discussions " height="280" width="179">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_39c250a9-d522-4b39-b86b-45774ab01cd6" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Discussions </strong>link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_discussion_topic" data-step-uuid="b7585ff6-b240-4b64-a8b7-1870dc1a1f6e">
    <h2 id="open_discussion_topic" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Discussion</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/698/374/original/1858cb39-d211-4fa8-8324-571408287b33.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
